snippet.title: $125 Donation 2 Fish Poke Bowls Challenge - Sponsored by Patrick Gillan
snippet.description:
Thanks Patrick for the kind hearted donation during the Sunday Live Stream of $125.  I used a little of that money to reward myself with 2 big bowls of Poke Fish from the local restaurant.  I haven't eaten like this in forever so thanks for making my day feel special.
